		(property "Description" "Raspberry Pi CM4 carrier board.  Footprints options of 0mm clearance and 1.5mm module clearance. Use connector DF40C-100DS-0.4v for short stackup hieght. Use connectorDF40HC(3.0)-100DS-0.4v for tall stackup height. Use standoff 9774015151R for short standoff options. Use standoff 9774030151R for tall standoff options. Options with Pads are connected to Pin 1 (GND) of CM connector."
